</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[227,1437,748,880]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
COLOURATION. Carapace (
<figureCitation box="[525,597,748,774]" captionStart="Fig. 2" captionStartId="5.[227,270,1966,1992]" captionTargetBox="[227,1436,581,1931]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[227,1436,581,1931]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Fig. 2. Ballomma erasmus gen. et sp. nov. A – C. Paratype, ♀. D. Holotype, ♂. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. As preceding, ventral view. C. As preceding, lateral view. D. Habitus, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1406676/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
